      <title>The SNL 50th anniversary special: What worked and what didn't</title>
      <author>Eric Deggans</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/02/17/nx-s1-5292384/saturday-night-live-snl-50-anniversary-special-takeaways</link>
